SHAREPERLTOPUS!

A perl library and command-line utility for gettting data out of SharePoint.

If you're more a Python person, you might also want to try python-sharepoint https://github.com/ox-it/python-sharepoint/.

The --where option accepts XML. For example :
  --where "<Eq><FieldRef Name='Category' /><Value Type='Text'>Trumpet</Value></Eq>" 


